thread.title_full: BRIEF-UMT United Mobility Technology H1 net income up at EUR 605,000 | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-UMT United Mobility Technology H1 net income up at EUR 605,000
text:
Sept 25 UMT United Mobility Technology AG :
* EBIT for the first half-year to 460,000 euros ($513,038) (previous year - after eliminating the non-recurring income - 105,000 euros)
* H1 net income in the amount of 605,000 euros (previous year: 206,000 euros)
* H1 revenues of 1.050 million euros (previous year: 0 million euros) Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: ($1 = 0.8966 euros) (Gdynia Newsroom)
